{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"cf4a438a-7ed7-4cf0-bd16-73a1a28b8bac","content":"Here's the full configuration:\n\n### Environment Variables\n\n| Variable | Value | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump` | `1` | Enables automatic dump on crash |\n| `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType` | `4` | Full dump (1=Mini, 2=Heap, 3=Triage, 4=Full) |\n| `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName` | `/dumps/core_%p_%t.dmp` | Dump path with PID + timestamp |\n| `DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath` | `/opt/tools/createdump` | Custom createdump location (required for NativeAOT) |\n| `DOTNET_EnableCrashReport` | `1` | Also generates a JSON crash report |\n\n### Pod Spec Changes\n\n```yaml\nspec:\n  containers:\n  - name: app\n    # ... existing config ...\n    env:\n    - name: DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump\n      value: \"1\"\n    - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType\n      value: \"4\"\n    - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName\n      value: \"/dumps/core_%p_%t.dmp\"\n    - name: DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath\n      value: \"/opt/tools/createdump\"\n    - name: DOTNET_EnableCrashReport\n      value: \"1\"\n    volumeMounts:\n    - name: crash-dumps\n      mountPath: /dumps\n    securityContext:\n      capabilities:\n        add:\n        - SYS_PTRACE\n  volumes:\n  - name: crash-dumps\n    emptyDir:\n      sizeLimit: 4Gi\n```\n\n### Key points\n\n- **`SYS_PTRACE`** is required — `createdump` uses `ptrace` to capture process memory.\n- **`DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath`** is essential for NativeAOT since the runtime can't auto-discover `createdump` like CoreCLR does.\n- **`emptyDir`** keeps dumps pod-local. Swap to a `PersistentVolumeClaim` if you need dumps to survive pod restarts.\n- Adjust `sizeLimit` based on your app's memory footprint — full dumps can be large.\n- Lower `DbgMiniDumpType` to `2` (Heap) or `3` (Triage) if full dumps are too big.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"f97e39c0-c32c-4aeb-ac6d-436546c8f9d0","outputTokens":617,"requestId":"204E:1A4FD7:74A1C3:874384:69F011DD"},"id":"d21596e8-a82c-450a-972e-9ccd80f93f8d","timestamp":"2026-04-28T01:48:25.107Z","parentId":"4a3011d7-1b4f-49fb-9238-eca7eae2d432"}
